{"tid":1220123,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆全港頌親恩圖畫填字大賽","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:54:35.000Z","uid":243252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"470b31d1c82dd20dfc4013c44df4a47570c7812c","tid":1220123,"uid":243252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"一路返工一路聽住啲茶水姐姐圍爐大大聲係到傳播示威者 收款暴動 , 抵死犯賤!<br />\n<br />\n放工遠離左港島位置, 眼見其實好大部份人仍然無動於衷, 再唔係憑大台播出嚟既片高談闊論<br />\n<br />\n結果花左少少時間同朋友整合左一堆圖片,<br />\n<br />\n而家準備印出嚟貼喺自己既社區範圍附近 希望比其他無關注既人睇到我地既<span style=\"color: red;\">犧牲, 付出 同他犬既兇狠 </span>既一面<br />\n<br />\n唔印出嚟 我建議都可以連同隔離POST 個長輩圖一樣 , share出去比所有人睇到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/14/102639_14ea85cb9fc46756ed3ff8484ea7f547.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2F102639_14ea85cb9fc46756ed3ff8484ea7f547.png&h=9162ee33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/14/102736_4b76057eec2e9588ff895a22e422cea1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2F102736_4b76057eec2e9588ff895a22e422cea1.png&h=9bc2eb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/14/102807_bce32a0ac2df9c5edc423f3680f260fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2F102807_bce32a0ac2df9c5edc423f3680f260fd.png&h=9e6a2555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4603e20886134f25c6b84dcb8e5990e8bfd9d9d","tid":1220123,"uid":243252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"每張圖都留左位置 去填大家想表達既訊息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}